data.description: Two structures on a large lot In sought-after Austell, Georgia, this 2 bedroom, 2 bath home which can easily convert to 3 bedrooms. Main house needs cosmetic updates and the auxiliary building needs a renovation but expands your options tremendously.  The list price is $20,000 below its recent appraisal. You can’t beat this square footage! Check the comps… the home is located in a vibrant community where property values continue to rise, this home is surrounded by higher-priced sales, hinting at its immense potential value for an owner occupant or investor.
